div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>(sraṃ)</span> 2000. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>sītya, -halya</span> <i><span>a.</span></i> ploughed in two ways, <i><span>i. e.</span></i> first lengthwise and then breadth-wise. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>suvarṇa</span> <i><span>a.</span></i> worth or bought for two golden coins. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>han</span> <i><span>m.</span></i> an elephant. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>hāyana</span>, <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>varṣa</span> <i><span>a.</span></i> two years old. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>hīna</span> <i><span>a.</span></i> of the neuter gender. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>hṛdayā</span> a pregnant woman. <div style='margin-top:0.6em;'></div></div><strong>—</strong> <span class='sdata'>hotṛ</span> <i><span>m.</span></i> an epithet of Agni.","evidence":{"band":1,"band_label":"core -- memorise","rank_all":120,"count_all":3788,"first_era":"Vedic","genre":null,"example":{"sa":"dve","ru":"две","work":"01_mahabharata-adiparva","passage":"1.2.130-135","kind":"translation","source":"corpus_lexicon.jsonl (pwg_ru Phase 4, SanskritLexicography/RussianTranslation)"},"badges":[{"field":"band","value":1,"label":"core -- memorise","source":"kosha frequency layer, rank_all (DCS archive.sqlite M9 via VisualDCS)"},{"field":"count_all","value":3788,"label":"3788 attestations in DCS","source":"DCS archive.sqlite M9 (VisualDCS)"},{"field":"first_era","value":"Vedic","label":"first attested: Vedic","source":"DCS archive.sqlite M9 (VisualDCS)"},{"field":"genre","value":null,"label":"genre sketch not derivable from current DCS extraction (only a chronologica